Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【開場語】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得明白一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  就算不說明白也是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  明白地說就是他們都死了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船  明白地說就是已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉絲應該能為他們做點什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒食欲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白地說 大人們全都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖不知是疫病還是什麼引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是不再活著了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再活著？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說生命活動已經停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是所謂的“死”這種東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 從剛才就一直在這樣說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於我並沒有活著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不明白“死”這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死是一切的結束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那比什麼離別都更痛苦

Comment: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:50.97,chop,,0000,0000,0000,,【OP：瞳の中の迷宫】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:11.25,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.50,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}思念越發強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.63,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無法傳達到這份祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:24.22,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}一定是因為	迷失了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:31.94,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無論何時  只有被映在這眼瞳裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:35.40,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}是唯一的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:38.57,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}一直如此堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:42.74,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}世界並非唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:46.50,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}還有所謂如果的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.50,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}因為存在著無限可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.13,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}正迷失著方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.88,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.89,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}不論你現在身處何處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.10,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}必定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:10.77,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}不慎闖入了瞳中的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.44,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:16.69,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被黑暗之手遮蔽了去路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:20.82,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被怯弱的心所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.62,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}也不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:27.20,chop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}繼續尋找著

Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:11.25,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.50,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}思いつのるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.63,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}この祈りが届かないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:24.22,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}何かをきっと 見失ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:31.94,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}いつだって この瞳に 映されたものだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:35.40,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}唯一の真実だと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:38.57,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}信じていたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:42.74,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}世界は一つじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:46.50,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}もしもという世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.50,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}無限にあるとして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.13,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}いま途方に暮れている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.88,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.89,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}いま何処にいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.10,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}必ず見つけ出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:10.77,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}迷い込んだのは瞳の中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.44,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:16.69,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}例え暗闇がゆく手を遮り
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:20.82,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}弱気な心惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.62,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}諦めないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:27.20,jpop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}探しつづけるから

Comment: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【對白】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fad(1200,1200)\be1\bord2\4a&Hc1&\3a&Hc1&\shad3\pos(470,370)}九尾狐妖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明確實地感受到了初美的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船結果也只是一艘移民船而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭！火箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球型的行星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去有幾條命也不夠用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉絲小姐 您去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 拉拉 你還有空間彎曲跳躍的能量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 如果只是跳躍一次的話 應該能夠...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在距這裡4光年的地方找到一個很好的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 葉月小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有這種森林存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為空氣很清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外怎麼說這裡也是露娜奧大人曾待過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜奧大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說露娜奧大人在百年以前 突然從這個森林裏出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時還是一個嬰兒 被作為神的孩子撫養長大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人後來怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救飛船 到船外進行作業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣被黑暗的宇宙空間吞噬掉 再也回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我所憧憬的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那也是在16歲的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你為什麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉曼那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉叫大家回到教室裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要進行空間彎曲跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間彎曲跳躍？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要突然要？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 感覺是個風急雲厚的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 瞧 那個星球簡直和地球一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兩百年間 我們一直進行著尋找能移民的行星的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已到了這一目標成為現實的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個行星是否適合生存將立刻進行檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快的話 幾天以內就將開始進行移民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請盡快將隨身的物品整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須給新的故鄉取一個名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得新的行星叫露娜奧最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沐浴在太陽的光芒中是怎麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有故障發生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於船外的自動行星探測裝置的部件 發生了故障
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要更換
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1區到4區的志願進行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船外作業的人請到各區的密封倉集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子太勉強了 我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呀 你不是文科的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是從拉拉那裡好好地學習過船外作業哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓蕾拉來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫出港的艙口 CO2單元發來的信號中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請將那個單元全部更換
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露娜奧大人  請守護我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉曼那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在那個星球上結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呀 太髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家將在新的行星露娜奧上開始新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船由於沒有著陸機能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請大家登上停放在各區內的小型著陸艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以突入大氣圈內
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快走吧 拉曼娜正在等你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼隨後再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們接著要怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們隨後會再去其他的世界 就此道別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們 不可思議的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是從拉拉那裡交給我保管的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是地球上各種各樣生物的DNA數據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了它 也就能讓地球上的動物們再生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快將進入發射狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各著陸艇確認安全帶狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美麗的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡著陸啊 拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉呢？拉拉不在這艘船裏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 這段錄音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉拉給你們的最後的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家送到這個行星後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部的使命也就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不忘記到現在為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起所學的各種各樣的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能創造出一個新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉將永遠地祈禱著那是一個美麗的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 我的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得很寂寞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 對我來說既沒有孤獨也沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間與永恆都是一種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在這裡永遠地注視著新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 雖然很突然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們再度回到宇宙庭園的書本中去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊不知怎麼總有一種因緣深厚的氣息...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉艾爾公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 不過我叫瑪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 瑪奧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 瑪奧過去的名字叫瑪莉艾爾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道！ 那種女人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 這孩子曾是一隻青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那確實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個笨拙的青蛙 想幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰的靈魂的化身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐 變成這種樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 相當漂亮的女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 也可能那樣會比較幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣她就待在了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你啊 臉上一幅這裡很痛的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼 你們這些傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙會游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的分身 怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓我好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是“分身”？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙最多不過是我的家臣罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你造出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有自由的東西無論怎麼想也是造不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 那三個人是你的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅凜 還記得她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我與那些傢伙相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真沒風度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己不能接受自己弱點 對男人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 對人來說是最沒風度的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱點！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被選中的應該成為這個世界的支配者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被選中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻為什麼到了現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 別說那麼多了 不如來陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是好大的屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 被褥晃來晃去 莉莉絲坐不正啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙庭園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像來到了九尾狐妖的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡迷路的話 也許就再也回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那樣…好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要初美在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 葉月 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為會死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褲衩還在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:17:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 格魯艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 被燒傷的地方開始痛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被海水浸多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊 好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去後要記著吃藥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:19:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那個女人真的是鬼啊 鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那就是鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰娶了她真是大禍臨頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大件事發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也空了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真能喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 不好了 格魯艾爾那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要結婚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到葉月啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子帽子的 那麼可怕啊 莉莉絲的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過份 把莉莉絲的帽子還來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然以前聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像也不是什麼厲害的角色嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺比起平常好像要軟弱得多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺比起平常好像要可愛得多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在假哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有假哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉絲明明沒做什麼壞事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是相當地吵鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初美！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃！

Comment: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:33.84,jped,,0000,0000,0000,,【ED：永遠の祈りを捧げて】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:41.57,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠の祈りをささげて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:48.28,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}大事なもの諦めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:21:59.21,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}どんなに遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:02.59,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}きっと捕まえてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:10.35,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}君と僕との それが約束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:17.40,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}思いでも 抱きしめないでいても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:24.82,jped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,220)}気持ちは 一つも届かない
